text.tspan: When you click Try Beaver reads the card in the cell
above him, then goes to the cell that has that number.
He keeps doing that until he reaches the flag, or ends in a loop.
Swap the position of two cards, so that Beaver
1 star: just get bebras to get to the end, 1 swap?
2 stars: 2 cycles, get bebras to reach the end in X steps, with 1 swap
4 stars: 7 cycles, end is in cell 1, 2 swaps
